<h2>About This Project</h2>

<p>
    This Project Management App was realized as part of the <strong>Software Engineering 2</strong> course, which is part of the fourth-year of the
    <strong>Computer Science and Software Engineering</strong> program, at the <strong>Faculty of Engineering Sciences, University of Kragujevac</strong>.
</p>

<p>
    The purpose of this project is to provide a simple, intuitive system for managing projects, work packages, task items, and tracking employees’ hours and contributions.
    It demonstrates knowledge in ASP.NET Core, Entity Framework Core, database design, and web application development.
</p>

