<h4>Technologies Used</h4>
<ul>
    <li>ASP.NET Core Razor Pages</li>
    <li>Entity Framework Core (SQLite)</li>
    <li>Bootstrap 4 for styling</li>
    <li>C# and .NET 7</li>
</ul>

<h4>Features</h4>
<ul>
    <li>CRUD for projects, work packages, task items, employees, and teams</li>
    <li>Timesheet tracking and progress calculation</li>
    <li>Detailed views for employees, teams, and projects</li>
    <li>Interactive navigation between related entities</li>
</ul>

